svg.title: The United States of America
svg.desc:
A simple game to help people learn the locations of US states. Created by Jon Relf (http://my.opera.com/orinoco/blog/find-the-country)
Original map from Wikimedia Commons (http://commons.wikimedia.org/)
Code help and suggestions from johnnysaucepn (http://touchthe.net/) and Jeff_Schiller (http://blog.codedread.com/)
